WEBVTT

00:01.213 --> 00:02.202
NARRATOR:
<i>Previously</i> :

00:02.373 --> 00:04.887
LORNE: A mystical pregnancy
right under my beak?

00:11.293 --> 00:12.885
GUNN:
<i>You're a Power that was?</i>

00:13.053 --> 00:15.044
ANGEL: <i>We're saved.</i>
CONNOR: <i>She's amazing.</i>

00:15.213 --> 00:17.602
LORNE: <i>Eternal bliss.</i>
WESLEY: <i>Tell us what to do.</i>

00:19.373 --> 00:21.091
FRED:
You're hurt.

00:21.253 --> 00:23.767
I scrubbed till my fingers bled,
but I couldn't get out...

00:24.173 --> 00:25.162
JASMINE:
Fred?

00:27.093 --> 00:29.049
I can't believe Fred's evil.

00:29.213 --> 00:33.650
We'll find Fred, but not tonight.
Tomorrow will be easier than today.

00:33.813 --> 00:37.647
<i>Good morning, Los Angeles.</i>
<i>Thank you for inviting me.</i>

00:37.813 --> 00:39.804
WESLEY: <i>If she's out there,</i>
<i>she's a threat.</i>

00:39.973 --> 00:41.406
We have to kill her.

00:43.000 --> 00:49.074
